y and a member of that boards compensation committeemr walls was senior vice president and general counsel for enrons domestic independent power business and later its international energy businesshe has extensive experience in europe asia africa india south america and central america prior to his enron experience he was a lawyer at vinson  elkins llp where he practiced energy finance and international lawhe serves on the boards of the texas childrens cancer center west houston young life and the chinquapin school executive vice president and general counsel of clear channel communications incmr walls received both his jd with honors and his bba from the university of texas at austin current positions of robert h walls jr  nametitle since clear channel worldwide holdings inc secretary  director  clear channel outdoor holdings incadvertising  marketing secretary executive vp  general counsel clear channel broadcasting inc secretary executive vp  general counsel iheartmedia capital i llc secretary executive vp  general counsel enron global assets  services inc managing director  general counsel  iheartmedia incbroadcasting secretary executive vp  general counsel iheart communications inc secretary executive vp  general counsel post oak energy capital founding partner  advisor  holdings of robert h walls jr  nameequitiesvaluation clear channel outdoor holdings inc cco advertising  marketing  usd iheartmedia inc ihrt broadcasting  usd robert h walls jr personal network  namelinked companies richard j bressler clear channel outdoor holdings inciheartmedia incclear channel worldwide holdings inciheartmedia capital i llciheart communications inc robert w pittman clear channel outdoor holdings inciheartmedia inciheartmedia capital i llciheart communications inc steven james macri clear channel outdoor holdings inciheartmedia inciheartmedia capital i llciheart communications inc scott d hamilton clear channel outdoor holdings inciheartmedia inciheartmedia capital i llcihear